    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "SYSTEM TIMETABLE\nEffective May 1 through May 31, 1999\nNew Destination-\nPhilly!\nOn ATA You're On Vacation™",
      "NONSTOP SCHEDULED SERVICE ROUTES\nDUBLIN\nSHANNON\n(6/99)\n25 years of great destinations,\nlow fares \u0026 priceless memories.\nFRANCISCO\nLAS VEGAS\nLOS ANGELES\nPHOENIX\nDENVER\nDES MOINES •\nMILWAUKEE\nMADISON •\nLANSING\nCHICAGO\n• DAYTON\nINDIANAPOLIS\nNEW YORK\nPHILADELPHIA\nDALLAS\nHONOLULU • MAUI\nST. PETE\nSARASOTA\nFT. MYERS\nORLANDO\n• FT. LAUDERDALE\nCALL YOUR TRAVEL AGENT,\nBOOK ONLINE AT ATA.COM\nOR CALL ATA AT\n1-800-I-FLY-ATA\nSAN JUAN\nCANCUN\n•... Operated by Chicago Express"
    ],
